data.description: Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 story home nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac. This home boasts 3 separate living areas, open floor plan, and a dedicated office study space. All bedrooms located upstairs for privacy and togetherness. Harness the power of solar panels for energy efficiency. Enjoy serenity with a subterranean belt for privacy, mature shaded trees, and a family friendly playground just down the road. Exceptional value awaits in this family-friendly gem!
